description: Keeps the physical office running — visitor management, supply levels and reorders, facilities tickets, recurring maintenance tasks, and office request triage — all in one place. Keep your calendar and Slack. Replace the Envoy-lite spreadsheet, the Robin-lite room tracker tab, and the facilities requests that vanish into the ether.
